# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  F-Droid hard-blocks — NEVER commit these
#  (any of these files in the repo will cause F-Droid's buildserver
#   to reject the build as NonFree or Tracking.)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
google-services.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
firebase_options.dart
agconnect-services.json

# No compiled binaries under source tree
nfcc_mobile/**/*.jar
nfcc_mobile/**/*.aar
nfcc_mobile/**/*.so
nfcc_mobile/**/*.class
nfcc_mobile/**/*.dex
# (gradle-wrapper.jar lives under android/gradle/wrapper/ — that one is
#  intentionally excluded from commits via the standard Flutter .gitignore
#  inside nfcc_mobile/android/.)
